  "keyFeatures": [
    "Hardware-agnostic Python interface for robot control",
    "Standardized LeRobotDataset format (Parquet + MP4) on Hugging Face Hub",
    "State-of-the-art policies: ACT, Diffusion, VQ-BeT, TDMPC, VLAs (Pi0, GR00T, SmolVLA, XVLA)",
    "Training and evaluation on real robots and simulation",
    "Unified Robot class interface across diverse platforms",
    "Support for multiple robots: SO-100, LeKiwi, Koch, Reachy2, Unitree G1, and more",
    "Vision-Language-Action models for robot learning",
    "Reinforcement learning with HIL-SERL",
    "Dataset tools for manipulation, visualization, and sharing",
    "Integration with simulation environments (LIBERO, MetaWorld, ALOHA)"
  ],
